Package gov.nasa.larcfm.Util

Class Matrix3x3

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.larcfm.Util.Matrix3x3
  • public class Matrix3x3
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a basic (and naive) implementation of an 3x3 (row x column) matrix of doubles, with associated functions. Vectors are treated as 3x1 matrices. These matrices are mutable.
